Installation:

1. run "php composer.phar update" in root directory of knowledgeroot
2. import dump to database ( dumps are located in data/dumps/ ): postgresql.sql or mysql.sql
3. import demo-dump to database: postgresql-demo.sql or mysql-demo.sql
4. cp config/app.ini.dist to config/app.ini
5. set database credentials in config/app.ini
6. set base_path and base_url in config/app.ini
6. open the public folder from knowledgeroot in your browser

Default admin login:
User: admin
Password: admin
